   Protected Music Converter is a software which allows you easily convert   
   your protected (or unprotected) music files to most frequently used     
   unprotected formats (WMA, MP3, OGG, WAV). Thus you can listen your music   
   on your iPod, burn them to CD, upload them on your cell phone, use them on   
   whatever device you want, even if it doesn't support protected content   
   playback. Interface is straight and easy to use, without flashy colours or 
   graphics. All you need to do is to add your protected files to batch list, 
   select desirable output format and press start button. Supported input 
   formats are: M4P, M4B, M4A, MP4, AAC, WMA, MP3, WAV, OGG, AU audio files, 
   AIFF and much more
